name: Grand Tiegjon Casino Chip
description: This one billion ISK value casino chip will be familiar to any high limit table player at the Grand Tiegjon Resort & Casino in Vellaine. Holographically dated to be valid only for the 95th Interstellar Mindclash Championship in October YC117, it is now invalid and worth only its weight in the crystallized Isogen that it happens to be laser cut from.
